CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eleven women, including one wearing light colored strapless dress with bow at bust and polka dot skirt, posed in Webster Hall with landscape mural, for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
